lete framework document, distribution records, training certificates.", "description_ar": "", "description_en": "Comprehensive privacy impact assessment framework implemented across the entity with standardized procedures."}, {"level": 4, "name_ar": "مُقاس", "name_en": "Measured", "evidence_ar": "", "evidence_en": "KPI dashboards, compliance scorecards, quarterly reports.", "description_ar": "", "description_en": "privacy impact assessment effectiveness is measured through defined KPIs. Regular monitoring and reporting."}, {"level": 5, "name_ar": "محسّن", "name_en": "Optimized", "evidence_ar": "", "evidence_en": "Improvement initiative reports, innovation documentation, external audit results.", "description_ar": "", "description_en": "Continuous improvement of privacy impact assessment through data-driven insights. Industry-leading practices."}], "acceptance_criteria": {"0": [{"order": 1, "text_ar": "لا توجد ممارسات أو عمليات privacy impact assessment موثقة", "text_en": "No privacy impact assessment practices or processes are documented"}, {"order": 2, "text_ar": "لا يوجد وعي بمتطلبات privacy impact assessment", "text_en": "No awareness of privacy impact assessment requirements"}], "1": [{"order": 1, "text_ar": "وعي أساسي بمتطلبات privacy impact assessment لدى أصحاب المصلحة الرئيسيين", "text_en": "Basic awareness of privacy impact assessment requirements exists among key stakeholders"}, {"order": 2, "text_ar": "يتم تنفيذ أنشطة privacy impact assessment بشكل عشوائي", "text_en": "Ad-hoc privacy impact assessment activities are performed reactively"}, {"order": 3, "text_ar": "يتم تطوير مسودات أو وثائق غير رسمية", "text_en": "Draft or informal documents are being developed"}], "2": [{"order": 1, "text_ar": "تمت صياغة سياسة privacy impact assessment والموافقة عليها رسمياً", "text_en": "privacy impact assessment policy has been formally drafted and approved by leadership"}, {"order": 2, "text_ar": "هيكل العمليات موثق لـ privacy impact assessment", "text_en": "Process str